<br>
She had never dreamed that she would one day have the honor to bear the crest of the Vampire lord, to stand tall and mighty alongside the ranks of the most powerful mortal Norrath had ever seen.  Now that her trials and training were complete, she was determined to do just that--to bear His banner into the greatest battles of Norrath, to be a part of Him, a part of Norrath's very history. To be <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">worth</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> something!  She remembered the sting of her mother's hands and the bruises she'd weathered from the fists of her father as they poisoned her mind, filling her with lies and spite.  They said she would never amount to more than a whore.  She laughed inside--Oh, what she would do if they could see her this day!<br>
<br>
A twig snapped below, and she remembered her duty, glancing down suspiciously.  A shadow flitted between two trees along the canyon wall.  Scouts of Kelethin!  Ha!  She would teach them to try to sneak into His nest!  When she brought their corpses to His throne, He would smile upon her.  And recognize her. And perhaps promote her, or invite her to dine with Him, and He would call her to him by night, and perhaps...  Her heart fluttered, and a flush crept into her blue skin.  Glancing down again, she watched one of the Elves step out cautiously into the open, and drew back a Shuriken.  Today, she knew, would be the day that her life became something far more than meaningful. Today, she would become great.  Today, she would become loved. Today, she--<br>
<br>
The initiate staggered back with a shriek as an arrow whistled through the dusk, ripping into her chest.  She lurched forward onto the edge of her cliff watch, gripping at the arrow's shaft  and feeling her own warm blood slide through her hands.  Though her heart was narrowly missed, she felt in her mind that it had shattered, and her spirit, her hope, and her pride seeped out of her with her blood, dropping with it onto the dirt, just another meaningless casualty of a war being fought for no reason.  Meaningless...<br>
<br>
The initiate looked up and could just see the form of the Ranger below, and saw her despair mirrored in the Wood Elf's eyes.  They were different and the same, enemies of one heart.  The initiate whispered a last haunting gasp of despair and fell, tumbling over the ledge with a tear still lingering in her dead eye.<br>
<br>
She was the first of many. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Kelisk Mae'Lokh</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Chancellor of Skathris Ven'Sho--Patriarch of Cabilis</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=355953&quot;"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Inspect Kelisk?</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=siava>Siava</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://eqsighost.netfirms.com/Siava/ball47.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Raven</span><br>  Posts: 232<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/19/02 6:34:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=427.topic&index=34>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...prey thoughts</span><hr size=1> This is to remind myself NOT to read new entries here before work. *sniffle* <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=grafireforgedawn>Grafire Forgedawn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 65<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/19/02 7:04:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/